La Salle (Venezuela) Trip to Aruba 1954

[Jul 10]
Aruba              3-2      La Salle
  [Aruba scorers unknown; Asso, Otero]
[La Salle: Elgezabal, Caballero, Clemente “indio” Ortega, Barrios, D´Ambrosio,
  Mario Fernández, Apolinar, Primo, Otero, Asso, Noya. Manager: Pedro Cabillón]

[Jul 11]
Aruba              2-2      La Salle 
  [Aruba scorers unknown; Apolinar, Asso]
[La Salle: Magyar (hungarian), Gregorio “pescaíto” Gómez (argentinian), Clemente “indio” Ortega,
